3.Write a shell script to rename all files in the current directory with numeric continuous value(Warning: Do this in a personal folder. Don't use Home directory) 
----------------------------->
	a=1
	for i in d*.txt
	do
		echo "$i"
		mv $i $a".txt"
		a=`expr $a + 1`
	done




